rder-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(229, 231, 235); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 0px; color: black; font-family: __fkGroteskNeue_598ab8, __fkGroteskNeue_Fallback_598ab8, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal">The existence of some market inefficiencies actually helps maintain overall efficiency, as it provides incentives for market participants to seek out mispriced securities, thereby pushing prices toward their fair values</span></font>.<span style="color: black; font-family: __fkGroteskNeue_598ab8, __fkGroteskNeue_Fallback_598ab8, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; display: inline !important; float: none"><font color="black" face="__fkGroteskNeue_598ab8, __fkGroteskNeue_Fallback_598ab8, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji" size="16px">In practice, markets likely fall somewhere between perfect efficiency and complete inefficiency. The degree of efficiency can vary across different markets, securities, and time periods. Regulatory bodies play a crucial role in maintaining market integrity and promoting efficiency by enforcing rules against insider trading and mandating timely disclosure of material information.</font></span>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
